@snnn you are right, we don't provide the name in the TensorProto in this case.
According to the spec, the name of TensorProto is optional, only one is required, which is initializer: https://github.com/onnx/onnx/blob/master/onnx/onnx.proto#L241

So in run_model, inputs should be passed in the right order. :-)

